(57, 1, 6, 40, 5, 16, 16, NULL, 'Faith and Good Works', 'This connection highlights the importance of good works as a manifestation of faith. Both passages emphasize that acknowledging and demonstrating good things leads to glorifying God.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
