(57, 1, 6, 46, 14, 25, 25, NULL, 'Manifestation of Faith', 'This connection highlights the acknowledgment of God''s presence in believers. Both passages emphasize the effect of faith being made evident through worship and recognition of good things in Christ.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
