(57, 1, 7, 64, 1, 3, 6, 'great joy and consolation in thy love', 'Joy in Love and Charity', 'This connection highlights the theme of joy derived from love and charitable actions towards others. Both passages emphasize the refreshing impact of love and truth on the community of believers.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
