(57, 1, 8, 49, 5, 4, 4, 'which is convenient', 'Convenience in Christian Conduct', 'This connection highlights the concept of what is ''convenient'' in Christian behavior. Both passages emphasize the importance of aligning actions and speech with what is appropriate and beneficial in the faith.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
